snippet.textDisplay:
Those people who cannot accept changes and do not understand creativity, please do not waste your time here. This song is out of your head guys, trust me. The only thing you can understand is either part A or part B , but you cannot accept or comprehend both the things fused together. This song is off the mainstream genre of India, which people like so much and so most people may not like it. But that doesn't give you any authority to judge such talented musicians. And I bet half of you cannot even speak Tamil in such a tempo, these guys just rapped the shit out of Tamil, such a difficult job. And some of you are like "RIP COKE STUDIO". What the hell! Just made me upset by reading such unruly comments!

Anyways, I enjoyed it and that's all that matters. Period!
